    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Route demo requests with HubSpot and Outlook and log the results\n\n**Pattern:** Lead Capture & Routing · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nRoute demo requests with HubSpot and Outlook and log the results. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual routing is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Lead Form Submission → Required Fields Present? → Remove Duplicate Leads → Enrich — Primary Provider → Primary Hit? → Merge Enrichment Paths → Score Enriched Records → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to lead capture & routing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating routing in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
